Cast Vella Lovell (Emily Price). Michael Rowland (Fred ‘Shred’ Taylor). Ravi Patel (Amit Patel). Grace Palmer (Victoria Sands). Gerry Dee (Templeton Dudge). Kelli Ogmundson (Dolores Stubb). Amy Goodmurphy (AM Dispatch). Alvina August (Dr. Summers). Dayah Brar (Addy). Kevin Bigley (Rick Doyle). Ryan Beil (Booth Operator). Paul Ferancik (Tech Geek). Stephen Adekolu (JT Wallace). Amanda Burke (Woman). Sandy Robson (Zookeeper). Camila Savia (Ridiculously Hot Woman). Azahna Dhillon (Daughter). John Procaccino (Jimmy Shaw). Elisa King (Wife). Ali Karr (Yogi). Chris Nowland (Police Officer). Neemish Parekh (Man). Jake Sheardown (Delivery Guy). Andrew Zachar (Priest)

Language English.

Producers Todd Giroux. B.F. Painter. Bob Fisher. Jake Fuller. Rob Greenberg. Tony Hernandez. Clark Mathis. Joel McHale. Brooke Posch. Tad Quill. Dan Sterling. Brad Stevens. Boyd Vico. Jim Brandon. Brian C. Singleton. Matthew Chipera.

Production Fox Entertainment.

Creators Bob Fisher. Rob Greenberg. Dan Sterling.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 5

Status OnGoing (2023–)
